    <item>
      <title>美国说，它正在推动加快台湾武器的运输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/us-says-it-s-pushing-to-speed-up-taiwan-weapons-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据事实上，美国正试图加快向台湾的武器发货加速，据事实上，台北驻台北的大使说，很可能会在台北向官员保证特朗普政府对乌克兰的军事援助担心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/us-says-it-s-pushing-to-speed-up-taiwan-weapons-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 02:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，“很快”的Tiktok交易中有四个投标人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/trump-says-four-different-groups-in-play-for-tiktok-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周日表示，他正在与Tiktok的四个不同可能的买家进行谈判，而社交视频应用程序的交易可能很快就会达成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/trump-says-four-different-groups-in-play-for-tiktok-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
